Routific,is,a,tool,for,scheduling,optimized,routes,for,fleets,of,vehicles,It,is,designed,to,help,reduce,the,number,of,trucks,and,drivers,needed,to,complete,routes,as,well,as,the,total,distance,traveled,Users,can,input,their,data,and,let,Routific,optimize,their,schedules,or,if,they,are,already,using,another,system,they,can,integrate,with,Routific,s,routing,engine,via,API